openapp-joomla (1.6.3-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Restart Apache after install so php actually works after
    a fresh install
  * Clear /var/www before installing Joomla. We expect only Joomla
    in /var/www. But do make a backup of the current /var/www
  * Fix permissions on /var/www
  * Fix a typo in openapp-joomla-passwd
  * Remove ${INSTALLDIR}/configuration.php.tmp after install

 -- Mark Schouten <mark@tuxis.nl>  Mon, 27 Jun 2011 12:21:04 +0200

